snippet.title: Corpse Party: Book of Shadows Trailer
snippet.description:
Missed the first one? Check out the trailer here
http://bit.ly/RXTjvI

The strange PSP adventure game is getting a sequel, throwing you back into the horror-filled world created by Team GrisGris.
